description: Clemondo Group AB is a chemical engineering company, which develops, produces, and markets cleaning and maintenance products. The company is headquartered in Kristianstad, Skane and currently employs 64 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2013-12-19. The company manufactures washing and cleaning products for home and industrial use, including automotive, food, workshop and hygiene. The firm cooperates with corporate customers in the Nordic countries and contractors in Austria, Poland, Czech Republic and Belgium. The company is also engaged in the development of private labels for other companies. The Company’s portfolio of brands includes Snowclean, Trutest, Strovel, HIAB, Duoex Chemical, Tellus and Marisol. The firm's customers include Statoil, Wallenius Marine, TT Line, Tvattlina and Volvo, among others.
naics: Soap, Cleaning Compound, and Toilet Preparation Manufacturing
name: Clemondo Group AB (publ)
